    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='228:255'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-1a' );" name="031-1a" class="pb">[031-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='255:269'>吕氏家塾讀詩記卷第三十一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='269:273'>魯頌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='273:294'>　孔氏曰此雖名爲頌而體實國風非告神之歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='294:335'><span class='krp-note'>朱氏曰其辭特以贊美當時之事其體猶烈國/之風非若商周天子之頌用於祭祀以歌詠先</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='335:345'><span class='krp-note'>祖之功/烈也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='345:370'>駉<span class='krp-note'>古營/反</span>頌僖公也僖公能遵伯禽之法儉以足用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='370:391'>寛以愛民務農重榖牧于坰野魯人尊之於是季</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='391:421'>孫行父請命于周而史克作是頌<span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰季孫行/父季文子也史</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='421:464'><span class='krp-note'>克魯史也○孔氏曰伯禽魯之始封賢君其法可/傳於後僖公名申莊公子閔公卒季友立之當惠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='464:491'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-1b' );" name="031-1b" class="pb">[031-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='491:534'><span class='krp-note'>王襄王時舒瑗云魯不合作頌故毎篇言頌名生/於不足也○曽氏曰季孫請命史克作頌恐是兩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='534:566'><span class='krp-note'>事如晉武公之大夫請命于天子之/使而作無衣請命作詩不相干也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='566:591'>駉駉牡馬在坰之野薄言駉者有驈<span class='krp-note'>户橘/反</span>有皇有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='591:619'>驪<span class='krp-note'>力知/反</span>有黃以車彭彭思無疆<span class='krp-note'>居良/反</span>思馬斯臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='619:647'>毛氏曰駉駉良馬腹幹肥張也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰腹謂馬/肚幹謂馬脅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='647:668'>　坰逺野也邑外曰郊郊外曰野野外曰林林外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='668:693'>　曰坰○曽氏曰坰野乃魯人牧馬之常地耳<span class='krp-note'>鄭/氏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='693:734'><span class='krp-note'>曰必牧於坰野者辟民居與良田也○李氏曰/坰之野其水草甚美旣不害於農又使馬得其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='734:758'><span class='krp-note'>所/養</span>○毛氏芣苢傳曰薄辭也〇毛氏曰牧之坰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='758:785'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-2a' );" name="031-2a" class="pb">[031-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='785:816'>　野則駉駉然驪馬白跨曰驈<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰孫炎曰驪/黒色郭璞曰跨髀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='816:851'><span class='krp-note'>間也然則跨者/所跨據之處</span>黃白曰皇<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰黃白/色雜名黃</span>純黒曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='851:891'>　驪<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰月令孟冬駕鐵驪象時之色檀弓/云夏后氏尚黒戎事乗驪故知純黒曰驪</span>黃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='891:922'>　騂曰黃<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰騂者赤色/謂黃而雜赤者也</span>諸侯六閑馬四種有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='922:956'>　良馬戎馬田馬駑馬<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰閑謂馬之所在有/限衛之處校人之注以爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='956:997'><span class='krp-note'>二百十六匹爲一廐每廐爲一閑諸侯有四種/其三種别爲一閑駑一種而分爲三閑也朝祀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='997:1032'><span class='krp-note'>所乗爲良馬征伐所乗爲戎馬/田路駕田馬駑馬給官中之役</span>彭彭有力有容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1032:1053'>　也○鄭氏曰坰之牧地水草旣美牧人又良飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1053:1074'>　食得其時則自肥徤耳○王氏曰彭彭張也〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1074:1101'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-2b' );" name="031-2b" class="pb">[031-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1101:1121'>鄭氏曰臧善也○孔氏曰薄言駉者有何馬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1121:1141'>乃有驈有皇有驪有黃此等用之以駕車則彭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1141:1161'>彭然〇朱氏曰思無疆言其思之深廣無窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1161:1198'><span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰僖公之思遵伯禽之法反覆思之/無有竟已乃至思馬斯善多其所及廣博</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1198:1227'>駉駉牡馬在坰之野薄言駉者有騅<span class='krp-note'>音/騅</span>有駓<span class='krp-note'>符悲/反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1227:1255'>有騂有騏<span class='krp-note'>音/其</span>以車伾伾<span class='krp-note'>敷悲/反</span>思無期思馬斯才</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1255:1287'>毛氏曰蒼白雜毛曰錐<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰雜毛是体有二/種之色相間雜上云黃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1287:1324'><span class='krp-note'>白曰皇黃騂曰黃止一毛色之中自有/淺深與此二色者異故不云雜毛也</span>黃白雜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1324:1362'>　毛曰駓<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰郭璞曰/今之桃華馬也</span>赤黃曰騂<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰周人/尚赤而牲用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1362:1389'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-3a' );" name="031-3a" class="pb">[031-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1389:1430'><span class='krp-note'>騂是騂爲純赤言赤黃者謂其赤而黃其色鮮/明者上云黃騂曰黃謂黃而微赤此云赤黃曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1430:1470'><span class='krp-note'>騂謂赤/而微黃</span>倉騏曰騏<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰謂青而微黒今之騘/馬也顧命曰四人騏弁注云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1470:1498'><span class='krp-note'>青黒曰騏騏/者黒色之名</span>伾伾有力也才多材也○王氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1498:1508'>　思無期思之乆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1508:1533'>駉駉牡馬在坰之野薄言駉者有驒<span class='krp-note'>徒河/反</span>有駱有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1533:1554'>駵有雒以車繹繹<span class='krp-note'>音/亦</span>思無斁思馬斯作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1554:1588'>　毛氏曰青驪驎曰驒<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰郭璞曰色有淺深/班駁隱鄰今之連錢騘也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1588:1621'>　白馬黒鬣曰駱<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰鬣/馬之騣也</span>赤身黒鬣曰駵<span class='krp-note'>孔氏/曰駵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1621:1656'><span class='krp-note'>是色名說者以駵爲赤色若身鬣/俱赤則騣馬故赤身黒鬣曰駵</span>黒身白鬣曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1656:1683'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-3b' );" name="031-3b" class="pb">[031-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1683:1714'>　雒○王氏曰繹繹屬也<span class='krp-note'>朱氏曰繹繹不絶貌/○毛氏曰善走也</span>○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1714:1735'>　鄭氏曰斁厭也無厭倦也〇蘇氏曰作奮起也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1735:1760'>駉駉牡馬在坰之野薄言駉者有駰<span class='krp-note'>音/因</span>有騢有驔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1760:1786'><span class='krp-note'>音/簟</span>有魚以車祛祛<span class='krp-note'>起居/反</span>思無邪思馬斯徂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1786:1823'>　毛氏曰隂白雜毛曰駰<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰郭璞曰隂/淺黒今之泥騘</span><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0686' title='KR0686' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0686.png'/>白</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1823:1860'>　雜毛曰騢<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰郭璞曰彤赤/也即今赭白馬是也</span>豪骭曰驔<span class='krp-note'>孔氏/曰說</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1860:1899'><span class='krp-note'>文云骭骹也郭璞曰骭脚脛然則骭者膝/下之名蓋謂豪毛在骭而白長名爲驔也</span>二目</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1899:1933'>　白曰魚<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰爾雅曰一目白瞷二/目白魚郭璞曰似魚目也</span>祛祛強徤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1933:1954'>　也○王氏曰思無邪一岀於正○鄭氏曰徂猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1954:1981'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-4a' );" name="031-4a" class="pb">[031-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1981:2003'>　行也○蘇氏曰孔子曰詩三百一言以蔽之曰思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2003:2025'>　無邪昔之爲詩者則未必知此也孔子曰讀詩至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2025:2046'>　此而有㑹於其心是以取之蓋斷章云耳〇吕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2046:2068'>氏曰僖公修牧馬之政以誠心行之故言思無疆思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2068:2090'>　無期思無斁思無邪馬之所以臧才作徂者其効</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2090:2112'>　也與衛風秉心塞淵騋牝三千之意同古之賢君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2112:2133'>　誠心以行善政其效皆若此然非獨牧馬而巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2133:2144'>　　　駉四章章八句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2144:2163'>有駜<span class='krp-note'>備筆/反</span>頌僖公君臣之有道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2163:2190'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-4b' );" name="031-4b" class="pb">[031-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2190:2215'>有駜有駜駜彼乗<span class='krp-note'>繩證/反</span>黃夙夜在公在公明明振</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2215:2238'>振鷺鷺于下鼔咽咽<span class='krp-note'>烏玄/反</span>醉言舞于胥樂兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2238:2265'>朱氏曰興也○毛氏曰駜馬肥強貌<span class='krp-note'>王氏曰養/之使駜也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2265:2300'><span class='krp-note'>○鄭氏曰僖公之用臣必先致其/禄食禄食足而臣莫不盡其忠</span>○孔氏曰四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2300:2321'>　馬曰乗○鄭氏曰早起夜寐在於公之所○歐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2321:2342'>　陽氏曰明明脩明其職也○毛氏曰振振羣飛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2342:2363'>　貌鷺白鳥也以興㓗白之士○歐陽氏曰振鷺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2363:2395'>　取其脩㓗翔集有威儀也<span class='krp-note'>朱氏曰鷺鷺羽之翿/舞者所持也下如飛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2395:2419'><span class='krp-note'>而下/也</span>○毛氏曰咽咽鼔節也○鄭氏曰于於胥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2419:2446'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-5a' );" name="031-5a" class="pb">[031-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2446:2467'>　皆也〇蘇氏曰在公明明言未始不在公也僖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2467:2488'>　公於是燕之以禮樂士之來者如鷺之集其醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2488:2509'>　者或起舞以相樂和之至也〇鄭氏曰僖公之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2509:2530'>　時君臣無事燕樂以遂其歡君臣於是皆喜樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2530:2534'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2534:2555'>　　有駜有駜興僖公有臣之壯盛也所謂君致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2555:2573'>　　其養臣盡其忠者蓋莫不在其中矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2573:2594'>有駜有駜駜彼乗牡夙夜在公在公飲酒振振鷺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2594:2609'>鷺于飛鼓咽咽醉言歸于胥樂兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2609:2636'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-5b' );" name="031-5b" class="pb">[031-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2636:2657'>　王氏曰牡剛強之材也○毛氏曰夙夜在公在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2657:2678'>　公飲酒言臣有餘敬君有餘惠〇鄭氏曰飛諭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2678:2687'>　羣臣醉欲退也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2687:2712'>有駜有駜駜彼乗駽<span class='krp-note'>呼縣/反</span>夙夜在公在公載燕自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2712:2731'>今以始歳其有君子有榖詒孫子于胥樂兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2731:2764'>　毛氏曰青驪曰駽<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰孫炎曰色青黒之/間郭璞曰今之鐵騘也</span>○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2764:2785'>　鄭氏曰載之言則也○李氏曰載燕亦飲酒也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2785:2806'>　○毛氏曰歳其有豐年也〇鄭氏曰榖善詒遺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2806:2835'><span class='krp-note'>蘇氏曰榖禄也臣願/其君冨且有後也</span>○朱氏曰頌禱之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2835:2862'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-6a' );" name="031-6a" class="pb">[031-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2862:2874'>　　　有駜三章章九句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2874:2907'>泮水頌僖公能脩泮宫也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰定本云僖公修/泮宫無能字○蘇氏曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2907:2950'><span class='krp-note'>此詩言作泮宫克淮夷閟宫言作新廟春秋皆不/載丗疑之泮宫閟宫僖公因舊而修是以不見於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2950:2993'><span class='krp-note'>春秋至於淮夷之功予亦疑焉然此詩有之式固/爾猶淮夷卒獲有所未獲而欲終之則其所獲尚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2993:3036'><span class='krp-note'>小也今此詩之言甚美而大則君臣之辭歟或曰/以君臣而爲此辭可也而孔子録之可乎曰維可</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3036:3079'><span class='krp-note'>之是以録之録其所可而去其所不可此孔子之/所以爲詩也子貢曰紂之不善不如是之甚也是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3079:3122'><span class='krp-note'>以君子惡居下流天下之惡皆歸焉孟子曰吾於/武成取二三䇿而巳以至仁伐不仁何其血之流</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3122:3165'><span class='krp-note'>杵夫二子之言信矣然孔子未甞以廢周書蓋好/惡之言必有過者要不以惡爲善則巳矣此逹者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3165:3175'><span class='krp-note'>之所自/諭也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3175:3202'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-6b' );" name="031-6b" class="pb">[031-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3202:3227'>思樂泮水薄采其芹<span class='krp-note'>其巾/反</span>魯侯戾止言觀其旂其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3227:3256'>旂茷茷<span class='krp-note'>蒲害/反</span>鸞聲噦噦<span class='krp-note'>呼㑹/反</span>無小無大從公于邁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3256:3277'>　毛氏曰泮水泮宫之水也天子辟廱諸侯泮宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3277:3318'><span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰辟廱者築土廱水之外圎如璧四方來/觀者均也泮之言半也半水者蓋東西門以南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3318:3359'><span class='krp-note'>通水北無也〇朱氏曰說文謂泮者諸侯郷射/之宫也西南爲水東北爲墻康成以爲東西門</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3359:3387'><span class='krp-note'>說文以爲東西/墻其說不同</span>○王氏曰思發語辭也○鄭氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3387:3408'>　曰芹水菜也樂僖公脩泮宫之水而往觀之采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3408:3439'>　其芹也〇毛氏曰戾止至也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰止者至而/止住故云至非訓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3439:3464'><span class='krp-note'>止爲/至也</span>○王氏曰觀其旂其物茷茷而有容聽其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3464:3491'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-7a' );" name="031-7a" class="pb">[031-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3491:3519'>　鸞其聲噦噦而有節<span class='krp-note'>李氏曰茷/茷飛楊也</span>○李氏曰無小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3519:3540'>　無大從公于邁國人無長㓜皆從公而往以見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3540:3561'>　國人從僖公之樂也○孔氏曰魯人作詩而自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3561:3577'>　稱其君爲魯侯者因其請王而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3577:3602'>思樂泮水薄采其藻魯侯戻止其馬蹻蹻<span class='krp-note'>居表/反</span>其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3602:3619'>馬蹻蹻其音昭昭載色載笑匪怒伊教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3619:3640'>　孔氏采蘋䟽曰藻水草也〇毛氏曰其馬蹻蹻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3640:3661'>　言強盛也〇鄭氏曰其音昭昭僖公之德音○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3661:3682'>　毛氏曰載色色温潤也○蘇氏曰僖公之至於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3682:3709'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-7b' );" name="031-7b" class="pb">[031-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3709:3730'>　泮宫好其顔色和其笑語未甞有所怒也教之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3730:3751'>　而巳〇王氏曰載色載笑則洪範所謂而康而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3751:3763'>　色者也夫然後能教也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3763:3784'>思樂泮水薄采其茆魯侯戻止在泮飲酒旣飲旨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3784:3799'>酒永錫難老順彼長道屈此羣醜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3799:3831'>毛氏曰茆鳬葵也<span class='krp-note'>釋文曰鄭小同云江南/人名之蓴菜生陂澤中</span>○鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3831:3851'>氏曰在泮飲酒者與先生君子飲酒也○毛氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3851:3872'>　曰醜衆也○蘇氏曰僖公與其羣臣飲酒於泮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3872:3893'>　宫咸願神錫之以難老使之順從長道以屈羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3893:3920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-8a' );" name="031-8a" class="pb">[031-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3920:3955'>　衆<span class='krp-note'>王氏曰順彼先生君子之長/道而屈服此魯國之羣衆也</span>○李氏曰一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3955:3976'>　言僖公之至泮水二章言僖公之教人三章則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3976:3997'>　又言至泮水與賢者飲酒也○朱氏曰比章以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3997:4007'>　下皆頌禱之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4007:4028'>穆穆魯侯敬明其德敬愼威儀維民之則允文允</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4028:4048'>武昭假烈祖靡有不孝自求伊祜<span class='krp-note'>音/户</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4048:4069'>　鄭氏曰則法也允文允武信文信武也○毛氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4069:4096'>　曰假至也<span class='krp-note'>朱氏曰假/感格也</span>○朱氏曰祖周公魯公也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4096:4117'>　靡有不孝信僖公之孝也無所不至也〇李氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4117:4144'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-8b' );" name="031-8b" class="pb">[031-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4144:4162'>　曰自求伊祜魯侯之福禄乃自求之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4162:4187'>明明魯侯克明其德旣作泮宫淮夷攸服矯矯<span class='krp-note'>居/表</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4187:4213'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>虎臣在泮獻馘<span class='krp-note'>古獲/反</span>淑問如皐陶在泮獻囚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4213:4233'>鄭氏曰克能攸所也言僖公能明其德修泮宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='4233:4254'>　而德化行於是伐淮夷所以能服也矯矯武貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='4254:4284'>　馘所格者之左耳<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰謂臨陣格/殺之而取其耳</span>淑善也囚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='4284:4304'>所虜獲者僖公旣伐淮夷而反在泮宫使武臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='4304:4325'>　獻馘又使善聽獄之吏如皐陶者獻囚言伐有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='4325:4346'>　功所任得其人〇孔氏曰王制曰天子將出征</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='4346:4373'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-9a' );" name="031-9a" class="pb">[031-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='4373:4394'>　受成於學出征執有罪反釋奠於學以訊馘告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='4394:4415'>　故僖公旣伐淮夷而反在泮宫也〇朱氏曰或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='4415:4436'>　謂僖公未甞有淮夷之功而疑此詩之妄蓋未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='4436:4457'>　甞深考此詩乃頌禱之辭冀其有是功耳下章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4457:4462'>　倣此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4462:4483'>濟濟多士克廣德心桓桓于征狄彼東南烝烝皇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4483:4508'>皇不吳<span class='krp-note'>音/話</span>不揚不告于訩<span class='krp-note'>音/凶</span>在泮獻功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4508:4529'>　孔氏曰濟濟然多士皆能廣其德心謂心德寛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4529:4551'>　洪並無𥚹躁○毛氏曰桓桓威武貌〇孔氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4551:4578'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-9b' );" name="031-9b" class="pb">[031-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4578:4611'>　狄彼東南逺服彼東南<span class='krp-note'>釋文曰狄逺也〇王氏/曰狄攘而逖之也〇蘇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4611:4645'><span class='krp-note'>氏曰古/狄逖通</span>○鄭氏曰東南斥淮夷<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰淮夷/在魯之東南</span>烝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4645:4666'>　烝猶進進也○毛氏曰皇美也○鄭氏曰吳譁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4666:4687'>　也○王氏曰不揚戢也○朱氏曰烝烝皇皇成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4687:4708'>　也不吳不揚肅也○鄭氏曰訩訟也無以爭訟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4708:4729'>　之事告於治訟之官者○王氏曰不告于訩和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4729:4750'>　也○李氏曰人心可謂廣矣惟爲血氣所使一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4750:4771'>　有毫髪之利則忿而爭其心於是乎隘矣惟其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4771:4792'>　心廣故其征伐有逖逺淮夷之功烝烝皇皇不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4792:4820'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-10a' );" name="031-10a" class="pb">[031-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4820:4837'>　吳不揚未甞爭訟惟在泮獻功而巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4837:4866'>角弓其觩束矢其搜<span class='krp-note'>色留/反</span>戎車孔愽徒御無斁<span class='krp-note'>音/亦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4866:4884'>旣克淮夷孔淑不逆式固爾猶淮夷卒獲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4884:4912'>　蘇氏曰觩弓徤貌<span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰言/持絃急也</span>毛氏曰五十矢爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4912:4953'>　束<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰荀卿云魏氏武卒負矢五十个荀則/毛氏之師故從其言鄭注大司冦束矢云古</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4953:4984'><span class='krp-note'>者一弓/百矢</span>○鄭氏曰束矢搜然言勁疾也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰/其發則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4984:5013'><span class='krp-note'>搜然而勁○蘇/氏曰搜矢疾聲</span>○朱氏曰愽廣大也○鄭氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='5013:5034'>　徒行者御車者皆無厭倦也淑善也式用也○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='5034:5055'>　蘇氏曰僖公兵戎精繕士卒競勸故能克淮夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='5055:5083'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-10b' );" name="031-10b" class="pb">[031-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='5083:5103'>甚善而不逆君子於是告之使益固其道庶幾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='5103:5113'>　淮夷可以盡得也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='5113:5138'>翩彼飛鴞<span class='krp-note'>于嬌/反</span>集于泮林食我桑黮懷我好音憬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='5138:5167'><span class='krp-note'>九永/反</span>彼淮夷來獻其琛<span class='krp-note'>勑金/反</span>元龜象齒大賂南金</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='5167:5187'>毛氏曰翩飛貌鴞惡聲之鳥也黮桑實也○鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='5187:5208'>　氏曰懷歸也言鴞恒惡鳴今來止於泮水之木</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='5208:5229'>　上食其桑黮爲此之故故改其鳴歸就我以善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='5229:5250'>　音○李氏曰喻淮夷慕泮宫之化也憬說文曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='5250:5276'>覺悟也○王氏曰琛寶也元龜尺二寸<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰/漢食貨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='5276:5304'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-11a' );" name="031-11a" class="pb">[031-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='5304:5332'><span class='krp-note'>志云龜不盈/尺不得爲寶</span>〇鄭氏曰大猶廣也○毛氏曰賂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='5332:5353'>　遺也南謂荆陽也○鄭氏曰荆陽貢金三品〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='5353:5374'>　孔氏曰淮夷來魯國獻其琛寶其所獻之物是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='5374:5390'>　大龜象齒又廣賂我以南方之金</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='5390:5402'>　　　泮水八章章八句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='5402:5435'>閟<span class='krp-note'>筆位/反</span>宫頌僖公能復周公之宇也<span class='krp-note'>蘇氏曰此詩/所謂居常與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='5435:5460'><span class='krp-note'>許復周公之宇者人之所/以願之而其實則未能也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='5460:5489'>閟宫有侐<span class='krp-note'>况域/反</span>實實枚枚赫赫姜嫄<span class='krp-note'>音/元</span>其德不回</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='5489:5510'>上帝是依無災無害彌月不遲是生后稷降之百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='5510:5538'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-11b' );" name="031-11b" class="pb">[031-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5538:5571'>福黍稷重<span class='krp-note'>直容/反</span>穋<span class='krp-note'>音/六</span>稙<span class='krp-note'>微力/反</span>穉菽麥奄有下國俾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='5571:5596'>民稼穡有稷有黍有稻有秬<span class='krp-note'>音/巨</span>奄有下土纘禹之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='5596:5599'>緒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='5599:5621'>　孔氏曰作者將美僖公追𫐠逺祖上陳姜嫄后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='5621:5642'>　稷至於太王文武爰及成王封建之辭魯公受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5642:5663'>　賜之命言其所以有魯之由○吕氏曰閟宫魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5663:5684'>　廟非姜嫄廟也言赫赫姜嫄者推本周家所由</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5684:5713'>　興○朱氏曰閟宫者魯之羣廟也<span class='krp-note'>毛氏曰先妣/姜嫄之廟在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5713:5754'><span class='krp-note'>周孟仲子曰是禖宫也〇孔氏曰大司樂云舞/大濩以享先妣以此知姜嫄之廟在周言其在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5754:5782'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-12a' );" name="031-12a" class="pb">[031-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5782:5822'><span class='krp-note'>周則魯無其廟姜嫄祀郊禖而/生后稷故名姜嫄之廟爲禖宫</span>閟深閉也<span class='krp-note'>毛氏/曰閟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5822:5846'><span class='krp-note'>閉/也</span>○毛氏曰侐清淨也〇蘇氏曰實鞏固也○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5846:5874'>　毛氏曰枚枚礱密也<span class='krp-note'>王氏曰枚/枚辨也</span>○鄭氏曰彌終也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5874:5895'>　赫赫乎顯著姜嫄也其德貞正不回邪天用是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5895:5916'>　馮依其任之又無災害不坼不副終十月而生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5916:5942'>　子不遲晚○毛氏曰先種曰稙後種曰穉<span class='krp-note'>孔氏/曰重</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5942:5983'><span class='krp-note'>樛稙穉生熟早晩之異稱耳非榖名也七月傳/曰後熟曰重先熟曰穉内宰鄭司農注云先種</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5983:6012'><span class='krp-note'>後熟謂之穜後/種先熟謂之稑</span>○李氏曰菽大豆○鄭氏曰奄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='6012:6033'>　猶覆也〇朱氏曰后稷生而享有百福播種五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='6033:6061'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-12b' );" name="031-12b" class="pb">[031-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='6061:6082'>　榖猶天所降也奄有下國堯封之邰也〇鄭氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='6082:6103'>　曰秬黒黍也○毛氏曰緒業也○鄭氏曰堯時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='6103:6124'>　洪水爲災民不粒食禹平水土后稷乃教播種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='6124:6141'>　故曰纘禹之緒美之故申說以明之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='6141:6167'>后稷之孫實維大王居𡵨之陽實始翦<span class='krp-note'>子踐/反</span>商至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='6167:6192'>于文武纘大王之緒致天之届<span class='krp-note'>音/戒</span>于牧之野無貳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='6192:6214'>無虞上帝臨女敦<span class='krp-note'>都回/反</span>商之旅克咸厥功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='6214:6236'>　鄭氏曰翦斷也大王自豳徙居𡵨陽四方之民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='6236:6257'>　咸歸往之於時而有王迹故云是始斷商○曽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='6257:6285'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-13a' );" name="031-13a" class="pb">[031-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='6285:6307'>　氏曰大王去邠居𡵨蓋諸侯之能興邦者本不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='6307:6328'>　必云肈王迹也武王旣有天下推其寖盛之由</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='6328:6349'>　故曰太王肈王迹所謂實始翦商者殆因肈王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='6349:6370'>　迹之語言之過耳聖人於武成猶有所不取者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='6370:6391'>　其於魯頌豈以一言之過而刪之乎○王氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='6391:6412'>　届至也天命不妄所廢興皆其至也致其至者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='6412:6433'>　武王也〇孔氏曰至於文王武王繼太王之業</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='6433:6454'>　於時商家暴虐天欲誅之武王乃致天之誅於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='6454:6475'>　牧野之地○鄭氏曰虞度也○朱氏曰無貳無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='6475:6503'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-13b' );" name="031-13b" class="pb">[031-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='6503:6524'>　虞上帝臨女猶大明云上帝臨女無貳爾心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='6524:6545'>　○鄭氏曰敦治旅衆咸同也○朱氏曰敦治而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='6545:6566'>　勝之也咸厥功輔佐之臣咸有功而周公亦與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='6566:6579'>　焉故下章言封伯禽之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='6579:6600'>王曰叔父建爾元子俾侯于魯大啓爾宇爲周室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='6600:6621'>輔乃命魯公俾侯于東錫之山川土田附庸周公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='6621:6642'>之孫莊公之子龍旂承祀六轡耳耳春秋匪解享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='6642:6663'>祀不忒皇皇后帝皇祖后稷享以騂犧是饗是冝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='6663:6684'>降福旣多周公皇祖亦其福女秋而載甞夏而楅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='6684:6712'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-14a' );" name="031-14a" class="pb">[031-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='6712:6749'>衡白牡騂剛犧<span class='krp-note'>素河/反</span>尊將將<span class='krp-note'>七羊/反</span>毛炰<span class='krp-note'>蒲包/反</span>胾<span class='krp-note'>側/吏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='6749:6772'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>羮籩豆大房萬舞洋洋孝孫有慶俾爾熾而昌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='6772:6793'>俾爾壽而臧保彼東方魯邦是常不虧不崩不震</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='6793:6805'>不騰三壽作朋如岡如陵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='6805:6826'>　毛氏曰王成王也元首宇居也○鄭氏曰叔父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='6826:6847'>　謂周公也東魯國也成王告周公曰叔父我立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='6847:6868'>　女首子使爲君於魯謂欲封伯禽也封魯公以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='6868:6889'>　爲周公後故云大開女居以爲我周家之輔旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='6889:6910'>　告周公以封伯禽之意乃䇿命伯禽使爲君於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6910:6938'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-14b' );" name="031-14b" class="pb">[031-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6938:6959'>　東〇導江鮮于氏曰錫之山川謂境内之山川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6959:6980'>　也孟子曰天子之制地方千里公侯皆方百里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6980:7001'>　伯七十里子男五十里凡四等不能五十里不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='7001:7026'>　逹於天子附於諸侯曰附庸<span class='krp-note'>王制/同</span>○王氏曰孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='7026:7047'>　子曰周公之封於魯爲方百里也地非不足也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='7047:7068'>　而儉於百里而周官以爲諸侯之地方四百里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='7068:7089'>　蓋特言其國也則儉於百里并附庸言之則爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='7089:7126'>　方四百里也<span class='krp-note'>李氏曰鄭氏據明堂位謂封以七/百里欲其強於衆國其說不然詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='7126:7167'><span class='krp-note'>人言大啓爾宇不過謂公侯方百里伯七十里/子男五十里三等雖不同惟公侯皆方百里居</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='7167:7195'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-15a' );" name="031-15a" class="pb">[031-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='7195:7219'><span class='krp-note'>上等/焉</span>○毛氏曰周公之孫莊公之子謂僖公也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='7219:7240'>　○鄭氏曰交龍爲旂四馬故六轡○毛氏曰耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='7240:7266'>　耳然至盛也〇鄭氏曰春秋猶言四時也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏/曰錯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='7266:7292'><span class='krp-note'>舉春秋以/明冬夏</span>○孔氏曰其車建交龍之旂承奉宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='7292:7313'>　廟祭祀所乗四馬其六轡耳耳然〇李氏曰享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='7313:7334'>　祀無有差忒○鄭氏曰皇皇后帝謂天也成王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='7334:7355'>　以周公功大命魯郊祭天亦配之以君祖后稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='7355:7376'>　其牲用赤牛純色天亦饗之冝之多與之福〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='7376:7410'>　毛氏曰騂赤犧純也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰牧人云陽祀用騂/牲毛之注云陽祀祭天於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='7410:7438'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-15b' );" name="031-15b" class="pb">[031-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='7438:7468'><span class='krp-note'>南郊是天子祭天/南郊用赤牛純色</span>○李氏曰皇皇大之至也明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='7468:7489'>　堂位曰成王以周公有勲勞於天下是以命魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='7489:7510'>　公孟春祀帝于郊配以后稷禮運曰魯之郊禘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='7510:7531'>　非禮也周公其衰矣孔氏以帝謂感生帝此則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='7531:7552'>　泥六天之說〇鄭氏曰周公皇祖此皇祖謂伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='7552:7573'>　禽也載始也秋將甞祭於夏則飬牲楅衡其角</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='7573:7604'>　爲其觸觝人也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰封人注云楅/設於角衡設於鼻</span>秋甞而言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='7604:7625'>　始者秋物新成尚之也○毛氏曰白牡周公牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='7625:7660'>　也騂剛魯公牲也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰公羊傳云魯祭周公/何以爲牲周公用白牡魯公</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='7660:7688'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-16a' );" name="031-16a" class="pb">[031-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='7688:7729'><span class='krp-note'>用騂剛羣公不毛何休云白牡殷牲也周公死/有王禮謙不敢與文武同也魯公諸侯不嫌也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='7729:7762'><span class='krp-note'>故從周制說文曰剛特也/白牡謂白特騂剛赤特也</span>○孔氏曰將將盛美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='7762:7783'>　也大和中魯郡於地中得齊大夫子尾送女器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='7783:7804'>　有犧尊以犧牛爲尊然則象尊尊爲象形也阮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='7804:7825'>　諶禮圖云犧尊飾以牛象尊飾以象腹之上畫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='7825:7862'>　爲牛象之形<span class='krp-note'>毛氏曰犧尊有沙飾也○孔氏曰/鄭司農云獻讀爲犧犧尊飾以翡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='7862:7903'><span class='krp-note'>翠象尊以象鳯凰此傳言犧尊者沙羽飾與司/農飾以翡翠意同則皆讀爲娑傳言沙即娑之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='7903:7939'><span class='krp-note'>字/也</span>○毛氏曰毛炰豚也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰封人祭祀有毛/炰之豚注云爛去其毛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='7939:7964'><span class='krp-note'>而炰/之也</span>○孔氏曰胾謂切肉○毛氏曰羮大羮鉶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='7964:7992'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-16b' );" name="031-16b" class="pb">[031-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='7992:8032'>　羹也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰大羮者煮肉汁不和鉶羮肉味之/有菜和者也大羮謂大古之羮鉶羮謂盛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='8032:8068'><span class='krp-note'>之鉶器其大羮/則盛之於登</span>大房半體之爼也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰大房/明堂位曰周</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='8068:8109'><span class='krp-note'>以房爼房謂足下跗也上下兩間有似於堂房/然知是半體者周語云禘郊之事則有全烝王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='8109:8150'><span class='krp-note'>公立飫則有房烝親戚燕饗則有殽烝如彼文/次全烝謂全載牲體殽烝謂體解節折則房烝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='8150:8175'><span class='krp-note'>是半體/可知</span>○鄭氏曰萬舞干舞也〇毛氏曰洋洋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='8175:8196'>　衆多也○李氏曰孝孫有慶孝孫得享其福○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='8196:8217'>　鄭氏曰俾使臧善保安常守也虧崩皆謂毀壞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='8217:8245'>　也○毛氏曰震動也騰乗也<span class='krp-note'>朱氏曰震/騰驚動也</span>○鄭氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='8245:8275'>　曰三壽三卿也岡陵取堅固也<span class='krp-note'>王氏曰壽考之/三卿爲公朋也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='8275:8303'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-17a' );" name="031-17a" class="pb">[031-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='8303:8336'><span class='krp-note'>○朱氏曰三壽未詳或曰/願公壽與岡陵等爲三也</span>○朱氏曰此言僖公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='8336:8354'>致敬郊廟而神降之福人稱願之如是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='8354:8387'>公車千乗<span class='krp-note'>繩證/反</span>朱英緑縢<span class='krp-note'>徒登/反</span>二矛重<span class='krp-note'>直龍/反</span>弓公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='8387:8424'>徒三萬貝胄<span class='krp-note'>直友/反</span>朱綅<span class='krp-note'>息廉/反</span>烝<span class='krp-note'>之升/反</span>徒増増<span class='krp-note'>如/字</span>戎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='8424:8449'>狄是膺荆舒是懲則莫我敢承俾爾昌而熾<span class='krp-note'>尺志/反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='8449:8470'>俾爾壽而冨黃髪台背壽胥與試俾爾昌而大俾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='8470:8491'>爾耆而艾<span class='krp-note'>五蓋/反</span>萬有千歳眉壽無有害</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='8491:8524'>　毛氏曰大國之賦千乗<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰司馬法成方十/里出革車一乗兵車一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='8524:8565'><span class='krp-note'>乗甲士三人歩卒七十二人計千乗有七萬五/千人與下公徒三萬數不合者此自謂計地出</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='8565:8593'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-17b' );" name="031-17b" class="pb">[031-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='8593:8634'><span class='krp-note'>兵非彼三軍之車也○鄭氏曰大國之賦適滿/千乗苟盡用之是舉國而行也故其用之也大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='8634:8675'><span class='krp-note'>國三軍次國二軍而已○李氏曰成出革車一/乗千乗之地方三百十六里有竒包氏注論語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='8675:8709'><span class='krp-note'>以謂古者井田方里爲井一井/爲乗百里之國通有千乗也</span>○朱氏曰英矛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='8709:8746'>　飾也縢繩也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰朱英絲纒而朱染之以爲/矛之英飾弓束以緑繩縢謂約之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='8746:8777'><span class='krp-note'>以繩非訓/縢爲繩</span>○鄭氏曰二矛重弓備折壞也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏/曰重</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='8777:8805'><span class='krp-note'>弓謂内弓於鬯/鬯中有二弓</span>兵車之法左人持弓右人持矛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='8805:8826'>　中人御大國三軍合三萬七千五百人言三萬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='8826:8847'>　者舉成數也○毛氏曰貝胄貝飾朱綅以朱綅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='8847:8887'>　綴之<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰貝者水虫甲有文章也胄謂兠鍪/貝非爲胄之物故知以貝爲飾說文曰綅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='8887:8915'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-18a' );" name="031-18a" class="pb">[031-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='8915:8945'><span class='krp-note'>綫也然則朱綅直謂/赤綫以連綴甲也</span>○孔氏曰烝徒増増進行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='8945:8966'>　之時増増然衆多○毛氏曰膺當也〇鄭氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='8966:8987'>　懲艾也○蘇氏曰可以當戎狄懲荆舒而莫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='8987:9023'>　禦也言其強也<span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰僖公與齊桓舉義兵北/當戎與狄南艾荆及羣舒天下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='9023:9064'><span class='krp-note'>無敢禦也○孔氏曰僖四年經書公㑹齊侯等/伐楚一名荆羣舒又是楚之與國故連言荆舒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='9064:9090'><span class='krp-note'>其伐戎狄/則無文</span>○孔氏曰設辭慶之使汝昌大而熾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='9090:9111'>　盛汝長壽而冨足髮有黃色之髮背有台文之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='9111:9132'>　背○蘇氏曰壽胥與試者願其壽而相與試其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='9132:9153'>　才以爲之用也○鄭氏曰眉壽秀眉亦壽徴〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='9153:9181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-18b' );" name="031-18b" class="pb">[031-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='9181:9202'>　孔氏曰無有害無有患害○蘇氏曰此章言僖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='9202:9223'>　公治其軍旅繕其車甲器械故其民無不欲其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='9223:9237'>　昌大壽考而託之以爲安也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='9237:9258'>泰山巖巖魯邦所詹奄有龜蒙遂荒大東至于海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='9258:9273'>邦淮夷來同莫不率從魯侯之功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='9273:9294'>　孔氏曰泰山之髙巖巖然泰山在齊魯之界二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='9294:9315'>　國皆以爲望也○朱氏曰詹與瞻同○毛氏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='9315:9351'>　龜山也蒙山也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰春秋定十年齊人來歸/鄆讙龜隂之田謂龜山之北田</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='9351:9391'><span class='krp-note'>也論語說顓臾云昔者先王以爲東蒙主謂顓/臾主蒙山也魯之境内有此二山故言奄有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='9391:9419'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-19a' );" name="031-19a" class="pb">[031-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='9419:9440'>　○鄭氏曰荒奄也大東極東也海邦近海之國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='9440:9454'>　也○朱氏曰願其有功如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='9454:9483'>保有鳬繹<span class='krp-note'>音/亦</span>遂荒徐宅至于海邦淮夷蠻貃<span class='krp-note'>武伯/反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='9483:9501'>及彼南夷莫不率從莫敢不諾魯侯是若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='9501:9534'>　毛氏曰鳬山也繹山也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰禹貢徐州嶧陽/孤桐謂嶧山之陽有此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='9534:9558'><span class='krp-note'>桐木/也</span>○毛氏曰宅居也○朱氏曰徐宅謂徐國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='9558:9579'>　也○鄭氏曰諾應辭也若順也○孔氏曰莫敢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='9579:9599'>　不諾有命則莫敢不應李氏曰惟魯侯是順</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='9599:9620'>　也○蘇氏曰龜蒙鳬繹魯之四山其餘則東南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='9620:9648'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-19b' );" name="031-19b" class="pb">[031-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='9648:9662'>　勢相聮屬可以服從之國也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='9662:9687'>天錫公純嘏<span class='krp-note'>古雅/反</span>眉壽保魯居常與許復周公之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='9687:9708'>宇魯侯燕喜令妻壽母冝大夫庶士邦國是有旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='9708:9717'>多受祉黃髪兒齒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='9717:9738'>　鄭氏曰純大也受福曰嘏〇毛氏曰常許魯南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='9738:9777'>　鄙西鄙<span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰許田也魯朝宿之邑也常或作/甞在薛之旁○孔氏曰桓元年鄭伯以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='9777:9804'><span class='krp-note'>璧假許田桓/公以許與鄭</span>○鄭氏曰燕燕飲也令善也朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='9804:9825'>　氏曰令妻令善之妻也壽母壽考之母也僖公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='9825:9846'>　娶於齊曰聲姜母曰成風〇孔氏曰冝其大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='9846:9874'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-20a' );" name="031-20a" class="pb">[031-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='9874:9894'>之與衆士祝慶使與之相冝也邦國是有魯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='9894:9915'>　邦國僖公常保有之〇鄭氏曰兒齒亦壽徴○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='9915:9936'>　釋文曰兒齒落更生細者也〇蘇氏曰常許魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='9936:9957'>　之故地而未復者也願其壽考以復魯之侵地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='9957:9972'>　冝其室家臣庶以保有其國也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='9972:10001'>徂來之松新甫之栢是斷<span class='krp-note'>音/短</span>是度<span class='krp-note'>待落/反</span>是㝷是尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='10001:10034'>松桷<span class='krp-note'>音/角</span>有舄<span class='krp-note'>音/昔</span>路寢孔碩新廟奕奕<span class='krp-note'>音/亦</span>奚斯所作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='10034:10049'>孔曼<span class='krp-note'>音/萬</span>且碩萬民是若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='10049:10070'>　毛氏曰徂來山新甫山也○孔氏曰僖公修造</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='10070:10098'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-20b' );" name="031-20b" class="pb">[031-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='10098:10119'>　寢廟取徂來之松新甫之栢於是斬斷之量度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='10119:10149'>　之○毛氏曰八尺曰㝷桷榱也<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰桷之與/榱是椽之别名</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='10149:10170'>　舄大貌路寢正寢也〇朱氏曰新廟僖公所修</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='10170:10191'>　之廟〇孔氏曰奕奕然廣大○鄭氏曰奚斯所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='10191:10222'>　作者教護屬功課章程也〇<span class='krp-note'>孔氏曰奚斯公子/魚也爲之主帥教</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='10222:10252'><span class='krp-note'>令工匠監護其事屬/付工役課其章程</span>○鄭氏曰曼修也廣也○</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='10252:10273'>　孔氏曰言廟甚長廣而且大〇朱氏曰萬民是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='10273:10283'>　若順萬民之望也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='10283:10304'>　　　閟宫八章二章章十七句一章十二句一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='10304:10332'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0017', 'SBCK', '031-21a' );" name="031-21a" class="pb">[031-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='10332:10352'>　　　章三十八句二章章八句二章章十句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='10352:10367'>駉四篇二十三章二百四十三句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='10367:10381'>吕氏家塾讀詩記卷第三十一</span><br/>
